Class KineticComponent

    com.vaadin.event.MethodEventSource, com.vaadin.server.ClientConnector, com.vaadin.server.Sizeable, com.vaadin.shared.Connector, com.vaadin.ui.Component, java.io.Serializable, IKineticComponent

    public class KineticComponent
extends com.vaadin.ui.AbstractComponent
implements IKineticComponent
    Content component for experiment editor's tab sheet tabs. Contains kinetic canvas (in the client implementation) used to draw experiments. Also manages experiment data structure.
    Author:
    SkyCrawl
